text: Margaret Court and Judy Tegart Dalton defeated Rosie Casals and Billie Jean King 6–4, 6–4 in the final to win the Women's Doubles title at the 1969 Australian Open. ==Seeds== # Rosie Casals / Billie Jean King (Final) # Margaret Court / Judy Tegart Dalton (Champions) # Karen Krantzcke / Kerry Melville (Semifinals) # Françoise Dürr / Ann Jones (Semifinals) ==Draw== ===Full draw=== ==References== ==External links== * 1969 Australian Open – Women's draws and results at the International Tennis Federation Women's Doubles Category:Australian Open (tennis) by year – Women's Doubles Category:1969 in Australian women's sport Category:1969 in women's tennis
